'''Carlos Miguel Harvey Cesneros''' (born 3 February 2000) is a Panamaian professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Midfielder#Defensive midfielder|defensive midfielder]] for [[Major League Soccer]] club [[Minnesota United FC]] and the [[Panama national football team|Panama national team]].

==Club career==
He joined LA Galaxy II on loan from Tauro F.C. in February 2019.<ref>{{cite web |title=LA Galaxy II acquire midfielder Carlos Harvey |url=https://www.lagalaxy.com/post/2019/03/06/la-galaxy-ii-acquire-midfielder-carlos-harvey |publisher=LAGalaxy.com |accessdate=7 March 2019 |date=6 March 2019}}</ref> On 26 June 2020, Harvey moved to the [[LA Galaxy]] first team.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.lagalaxy.com/news/la-galaxy-acquire-midfielder-carlos-harvey-loan-la-galaxy-ii|title=LA Galaxy acquire midfielder Carlos Harvey on loan from LA Galaxy II &#124; LA Galaxy|website=lagalaxy}}</ref> He joined LA Galaxy on a permanent basis on 17 February 2021.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.mlssoccer.com/news/la-galaxy-sign-midfielder-carlos-harvey-panamas-tauro-fc|title=LA Galaxy sign midfielder Carlos Harvey from Panama's Tauro FC &#124; MLSSoccer.com|website=mlssoccer}}</ref>

Harvey signed with [[Phoenix Rising FC]] on February 7, 2023.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.phxrisingfc.com/news/phoenix-rising-signs-midfielder-carlos-harvey/ |title=Phoenix Rising Signs Midfielder Carlos Harvey |publisher=Phoenix Rising Communications |first=Jason |last=Minnick |date=February 7, 2023 |access-date=February 7, 2023}}</ref>

Harvey transferred to [[Major League Soccer]] club [[Minnesota United FC|Minnesota United]] on 24 January 2024.<ref>{{cite web |last1=Minnick |first1=J. |title=Phoenix Rising FC Rising Transfers Carlos Harvey to MLS side, Minnesota United |url=https://www.phxrisingfc.com/news/phoenix-rising-fc-rising-transfers-carlos-harvey-to-mls-side-minnesota-united/ |website=PHXRisingFC.com |publisher=[[Phoenix Rising FC|Phoenix Rising]] |access-date=24 January 2024}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Minnesota United Signs Midfielder Carlos Harvey |url=https://www.mnufc.com/news/minnesota-united-signs-midfielder-carlos-harvey |website=MNUFC.com |publisher=[[Minnesota United FC|Minnesota United]] |access-date=24 January 2024}}</ref>

==International career==
Harvey participated at the [[2018 CONCACAF U-20 Championship]] in November 2018. He made his senior international debut for Panama against United States on 27 January 2019 in a friendly match at the [[State Farm Stadium]] in Glendale, Arizona.<ref>{{cite web |title=United States vs. Panama – 28 January 2019 – Soccerway |url=https://int.soccerway.com/matches/2019/01/27/world/friendlies/united-states-of-america/panama/2944650/ |website=soccerway.com |accessdate=7 March 2019 |date=27 January 2019}}</ref>

